cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.AR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it focuses on generating state-of-the-art architectures on ImageNet. It also involves machine learning (cs.LG) as it uses a multi-objective reinforced evolutionary search backend. Additionally, it involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it uses neural architecture search to generate architectures. It also involves neural networks (cs.NE) as it uses a supernet to rank models. Finally, it may belong to the computer architecture (cs.AR) sub-category as it involves designing and evaluating neural network architectures.
